sequenceDiagram
    participant Touch as GameTouch
    participant Block as GameBlock(两块)
    participant GM as GameManager
    participant MM as MapManager
    participant Path as LinePath
    participant Act as GameAction
    participant Col as CollapseUtil

    Touch->>Touch: onTouchEnd → 命中首/次块
    Touch->>MM: 读取 board 并加边界
    Touch->>Touch: 校验同图案 + 可连线(≤2转折)
    alt 可连线
      Touch->>Path: drawPath(path, ...)
      Touch->>Act: emit UIGame_linkupAction(rm)
      Touch->>Block: setSelect(true) → connect(爆炸收缩)
      Touch->>GM: 更新计数/连击Tip
      Touch->>MM: 标记两块清除
      Touch->>Col: 计算坍塌交换并聚合 tween
      Col-->>Block: tween 到目标位，sleepTime 保护
    else 失败
      Touch->>Block: shake/错误提示(包围/转折过多/引导)
      Touch->>GM: 统计错误次数用于引导节奏
    end

